top, but spoke to foreign journalists; "If I had wanted to protect myself, I 
would certainly not have spoken out." Peter Charlesworth / J B Pictures; Photo, 
COLOR, Above, Fang and his wife, physicist Li Shuxian, at Cambridge University 
in England, where Fang accepted a position as a Royal Society Guest Professor. 
