<P>
CONAN THE INVENTOR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
For years I've been telling my friends that Arnold Schwarzenegger invented the 
phonograph, the electric light bulb, etc.; that Arnold used the pseudonym 
Thomas Edison because Schwarzenegger wouldn't fit on the patent application. 
</P>
<P>
Thanks for setting the record straight with the excellent photograph on Page 6 
of the Sept. 2 Book Review (see above right). 
</P>
<P>
STEVE YOUNGER 
</P>
<P>
LOS ANGELES 
</P>
