KUWAIT; JORDAN -- RELIEF; UNITED NATIONS -- JORDAN; IRAQ -- FOREIGN RELATIONS 
-- KUWAIT; IRAQ -- ARMED FORCES -- KUWAIT; MILITARY CONFRONTATIONS 
</P>
