<HEADLINE>
<P>
SOROPTIMIST PROGRAM SEEKING APPLICANTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Applications are now being accepted for the Soroptimist TAP (Training Award 
Program) Award. 
</P>
<P>
The cash award is given each spring by Soroptimist International of Manhattan 
Beach to a woman who needs assistance in getting training to enter, re-enter or 
improve her position in the labor force. 
</P>
<P>
Preferred candidates are heads of households who are completing undergraduate 
programs or entering vocational or technical training. The winner will be 
eligible for additional funds from Soroptimist Camino Real. For additional 
information, call 379-7798. 
</P>
