<HEADLINE>
<P>
GROUP HOSTS BENEFIT GOLF TOURNAMENT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A golf outing on Wednesday will begin two charity events by the Las Mariquitas 
Auxiliary of the San Pedro-Palos Verdes Assistance League. 
</P>
<P>
All proceeds from the "Flights of Fancy" events will benefit the chapter's 
philanthropies, including a dental center, a club for visually handicapped 
people and Operation School Bell, which provides new clothes for needy 
children. 
</P>
<P>
The golf tournament will take place Wednesday at Los Verdes Golf Club, 7000 W. 
Los Verdes Drive in Rancho Palos Verdes. It will be followed by a cocktail and 
prize party. For information and reservations, call 541-6708. The cost is $80. 
</P>
<P>
