In the Arrowhead League: 
</P>
<P>
Capistrano Valley Christian 54, La Verne Lutheran 0 -- Senior Brian Biegert 
rushed 26 times for 220 yards and scored three touchdowns to lead Capistrano 
Valley Christian (2-3, 2-0 in the league) at Laguna Beach High School. 
Capistrano Valley built a 21-0 lead by halftime on two touchdown passes from 
Chris Turner to Joe Hofferer and a one-yard run by Biegert. 
</P>
