<HEADLINE>
<P>
CITY ATTY. MYERS IS 'COMPETENT, DECENT' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I commend Julio Moran on his article "Political Brawl Over Homeless," Sept. 27. 
</P>
<P>
He did an excellent job of describing the situation in Santa Monica. 
</P>
<P>
As a 14-year resident, I would like to add my own observation about City Atty. 
Robert Myers. He is a very competent attorney and a person who behaves in a 
strikingly decent manner which transcends politics. He has always put his 
reputation where his beliefs are. One cannot help but admire such an 
individual. There are few in public office. 
</P>
<P>
NAN LEWIS 
</P>
<P>
Santa Monica 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
