examines the herb as it dries on racks at a Halder, Wis. farm.And an array of 
products that are made from ginseng. Associated Press; Photo, Rebecca Choi of 
San Diego makes a selection at Fung Tai ginseng store in Los Angeles. ; Photo, 
A traditional ginseng display jar. ROBERT GABRIEL / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
